/*
 * Author: Garth 'L-H' de Wet
 * Performs the dial tones and detonation of explosive.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: Unit to do dialing <OBJECT>
 * 1: Index <NUMBER>
 * 2: Dialing points <ARRAY>
 * 3: IED code <STRING>
 *
