/*
 * Author: esteldunedain
 * Creates an isolated ACE action
 * Note: This function is NOT global.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: Action name <STRING>
 * 1: Name of the action shown in the menu <STRING>
 * 2: Icon <STRING>
 * 3: Statement <CODE>
 * 4: Condition <CODE>
 * 5: Insert children code <CODE> (Optional)
