/*
 * Author: Glowbal
 * Spawns litter for the treatment action on the ground around the target
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: The Caller <OBJECT>
 * 1: The target <OBJECT>
 * 2: The treatment Selection Name <STRING>
 * 3: The treatment classname <STRING>
